{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when he was denounced and taken to Prague, they told him, if you tell us who else you did those things for, you can go back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If not, you go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he gave them my mother and my aunt's name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And by the time I came to my mother's room and my aunt's room, they were already gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the Gestapo had picked them up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was one building in Terezin in the center where the park was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was a German command building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in the basement, they had bunkers, and that's where they had put them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] I found out that to go down in order to be able to talk to my mother and see her, I could volunteer to go down and clean in the, in the building.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this way, I also got downstairs and saw her for a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was nothing I could do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then she and her sister were sent to the small fortress, which is in walking distance from Terezin and one of the worst prisons where rarely anybody ever got out alive, which they didn't, either.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the man himself was sent in the next transport to Auschwitz and never had a chance because they used the people to get information.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But then they didn't let them live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They immediately tried to do away with them, which, you know, I guess they never thought of that, never believed it and sought to save themselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there were, unfortunately, some who did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And my mother and aunt paid for, for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, after that, I got married in Terezin to a very nice man who came from a small town called Urmitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were married by rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
